data.description: Discover Homestead Bliss! This 4-bed, 2.5-bath haven is the epitome of modern comfort. With an open layout, the home exudes warmth and sophistication. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting stainless steel appliances and perfect for entertaining. Retreat to the spacious master suite with a spa-like ensuite. Outside, a large pool awaits in the manicured backyard—ideal for serene relaxation. Attached garage adds convenience. Located in Homestead, close to parks, top schools, and amenities. Your dream lifestyle starts here. Schedule a tour and seize this Homestead gem!
